(2, 'wsphome', 'JOB FOR THE POST OF BDO', 'Not Decied', 'careers@ashtexsolutions.com', 'Effective communication skills and must possess creativity to explain scenarios both verbally and written.', 'Lahore,Pakistan', 'Not Mention', '2016-05-09 00:00:00', '2016-05-20 00:00:00', 'jobspic/dd.jpg', 'Ashtex Solutions is looking for a female Graduate (BSC , BCS ,BIT , BSCS , BSIT , BBIT) for the position of "Business Development \r\n', 1),
(3, 'wsphome', 'Job For The Post of S.E.O Manager', ' 4-5 years', 'qamaradeel.emenac@gmail.com', 'Excellent Accent and English Communication Skills', 'Lahore,Pakistan', 'No', '2016-05-10 00:00:00', '2016-05-21 00:00:00', 'jobspic/ddd.PNG', 'Emenac Inc. SEO Manager Required the person have minimum 4-5 years of working experience and covering all possible aspects of S.E.O.Market competitive salary will be offered for this positions.The person have well understand about how we rank a website and how we got traffic on site and other SEO related task like keywords plan,researching about keywords. Emenac is a hub of well experienced professionals coming from different educational backgrounds. It is thus able to provide business owners with unparalleled assistance in business process outsourcing and opportunities to examine the issues or needs facing their businesses to seek assistance and make use of its finely designed solutions.', 1),
(4, 'wsphome', 'Senior Game Developers Required (ANDROID ONLY)', '3-4 Years', 'hr@regexsoft.com', 'OOP,Racing Games development', 'Lahore,Pakistan', 'No', '2016-05-20 00:00:00', '2016-05-31 00:00:00', 'jobspic/xx.PNG', 'Regexsoft is Requiring 3D Game developer for android games.\r\nPreferable technology is "Libgdx".\r\nAn ideal candidate must possess:\r\n1) A bachelor/master degree OR equivalent in the field of computer sciences. \r\n2) At least 3 to 4 years of experience in the industry (Android Platform).\r\n3) Very good OOP concepts and able to write memory efficient optimized code.\r\n4) Experience in Racing Games development is a BIG Plus.\r\n*****Why you join Regexsoft *****\r\n1) We are providing attractive salary package to ideal candidate and an environment that no one is offering in the industry.\r\nRegexsoft family is very happy and satisfied with its management and office culture and we are continuously enhancing it.\r\n2) Fuel allowance , Medical allowance, mobile allowance will be provided.\r\n3) Company sponsored lunch facility.\r\n4) Flexible working hours.\r\n5) No late sittings and work on weekends. \r\n6) Performance Bonuses and Products profit sharing. \r\n7) Job security.\r\nKindly Email your resume with portfolio to click apply button.', 1),
(5, 'wsphome', 'Paid HR Internship Oppertunity', 'Fresh', 'hr@bluegroupofcompanies.com', 'Managment', 'Lahore,Pakistan', 'No', '2016-05-24 00:00:00', '2016-05-30 00:00:00', 'jobspic/bgc.PNG', 'An emerging group of companies based in Lahore (TECH Society) requires an HR Intern for Second Shift from 03:00pm â€“ 12:00am.\r\nThe desired candidate should be at least a fresh graduate with BBA (HR) degree from a renowned university. Prior HR related internship or work experience will be an added plus. It will be a paid internship. \r\nInterested candidates are required to send an updated CV click on Apply Button before 30-05-2016.\r\nAlhamdulilah! Blue Group of companies started its operations in 1998 from Lahore, Pakistan. It began by providing Architectural design and construction services to the local. market. In the year 2005, the group emerged in the global market as a leading provider of online printing services along with other IT related services.\r\n\r\nBased on its experience of the international market In year 2010, the group added to its portal a complete setup of in-house printing and production setup and offered services to the local market under the name of Blue Media.', 1),
(7, 'wsphome', 'Graphic & Front End developer', '2-3 Years', 'hr@bluegroupofcompanies.com', 'Web Devl,Graphic Designing', 'Lahore,Pakistan', '30K-35K', '2016-05-24 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 00:00:00', 'jobspic/bgc.PNG', 'A group of companies (Lahore based) requires services of a Graphic designer/Web designer (Front End developer). The ideal candidate must be creative and able to think out of the box. \r\nGender: Male \r\nShift: Night \r\n(Freelancers can also apply) \r\nInterested candidates meeting requirements should apply.\r\nAlhamdulilah! Blue Group of companies started its operations in 1998 from Lahore, Pakistan. It began by providing Architectural design and construction services to the local. market. In the year 2005, the group emerged in the global market as a leading provider of online printing services along with other IT related services.\r\n\r\nBased on its experience of the international market In year 2010, the group added to its portal a complete setup of in-house printing and production setup and offered services to the local market under the name of Blue Media.', 1),
(8, 'wsphome', 'Senior PHP Developer Required', '5+ years', 'jobs@tekfirst.co.uk', 'PHP, PHP5, MySQL, JQuery, JSON, CSS, HTML', 'Lahore,Pakistan', 'No', '2016-05-24 00:00:00', '2016-06-08 00:00:00', 'jobspic/tk.PNG', 'Senior PHP Developer\r\nTekfirst is looking for a Senior PHP Developer to join their growing development team in Lahore Office.\r\n5+ years of experience in PHP, PHP5, MySQL, JQuery, JSON, CSS, HTML and AJAX \r\nAdvance knowledge of Native Javascript, preferred libraries are (jQuery, Backbone.js, Modernizer, require.js, Node.js, Web Sockets). \r\nExperience of complex SQL queries and database scheme design \r\nAdvance knowledge of MVC (Laravel , codeigniter, Zend framework 2).\r\nRelevant and interested candidates should send their CV on Click Apply Button. \r\nTekfirst is first4it provide specialist network support, Network Installations and Computer Support to many businesses across the region including venues such as the Conference Centre, Yorkshire Showground and major HOTEL and businesses in the region.', 1),
(9, 'wsphome', 'Business System Analyst Required', 'Not Decied', 'careers@i3RL.com', 'Data Handling', 'Lahore,Pakistan', 'No', '2016-05-24 00:00:00', '2016-06-09 00:00:00', 'jobspic/ii.PNG', 'Job opening for Business System Analyst in Lahore I3RL (Pvt.) Ltd. is developing innovative software solutions over Microsoft and Android technologies for leading UK Customers.\r\nPlease send your resume to click on apply button.\r\ni3RL or as we call it â€œThrillâ€ is a young and energetic organisation. At i3RL, we pride ourselves on providing innovative software solutions and services over Microsoft and Android technologies. Our high performance products particularly benefit small and medium sized companies who wish to gain that competitive edge over other companies in their field at an affordable cost. ', 1),
(10, 'wsphome', 'Multi Unit Manager Required', '7-9 Years', 'hr1@the-aagroup.com', 'Food', 'Lahore,Pakistan', 'No', '2016-05-25 00:00:00', '2016-06-04 00:00:00', 'jobspic/dd.PNG', 'Join Our Team!\r\nAA Group, a leading international business house, is currently hiring for its existing and upcoming outlets in Pakistan.\r\nQualification: Masters Degree\r\nExperience 7 - 9 years, with exposure of minimum 5 stores under supervision\r\nFunctional Area: International Food Franchise\r\nNo. of Positions: 1\r\nLocation: Lahore\r\nSuitable candidates can apply on click the apply button.\r\n\r\nSince the year of inception every company that is part of the AA group aspires to set new standards of excellence. With this vision in mind, AA Group seeks to become a global leader in trading & services.', 1),
(11, 'wsphome', 'Paid Administrative Internships', 'Fresh', 'awais.ahsan@nxb.com.pk', 'No', 'Lahore,Pakistan', 'No', '2016-05-25 00:00:00', '2016-06-04 00:00:00', 'jobspic/gg.PNG', 'Nextbridge Pvt. Ltd. is currently looking for â€ŽAdministrativeâ€¬ â€ªInternsâ€¬ at Nextbridge Pvt. Ltd. \r\nQualifications: BA/B.Com \r\nExperience: Fresh \r\nLocation: â€ª#â€ŽLahoreâ€¬ \r\nThis is paid internship. \r\nIf you are open to job market you can send resume on click the apply button.  \r\n\r\nNextbridge began as a one-man company, by the founder Mubashir Mian himself. We have been working in multiple development technologies since our inception in 1996; staying at par with the latest trends and demands of the industry. Besides being trusted by some multinational business giants, most of our work has been for Entrepreneurs passionate to make their mark in the world. One such highflier is International Checkout, which started in a garage, but is now recognized as an Inc. 500 Company in the U.S. And guess what? We are still working for them.', 1),
(12, 'wsphome', 'Sales Executive Required', '1-2 Years', 'aoonuos2013@gmail.com', 'Sales', 'Lahore,Pkistan', 'Negotiable', '2016-05-27 00:00:00', '2016-06-06 00:00:00', 'jobspic/right.PNG', 'Sales executive required at rightjobs.pk candidate should have own conveyance salary negotiable benefits include traveling allowance,medical,commission  and provident fund.The candidate must have sales experience in IT field.\r\nJob Duties:\r\nServices existing accounts, obtains orders, and establishes new accounts by planning and organizing daily work schedule to call on existing or potential sales outlets and other trade factors.\r\nAdjusts content of sales presentations by studying the type of sales outlet or trade factor.\r\nFocuses sales efforts by studying existing and potential volume of dealers.\r\nSubmits orders by referring to price lists and product literature.\r\nKeeps management informed by submitting activity and results reports, such as daily call reports, weekly work plans, and monthly and annual territory analyses.', 1),
(13, '', 'Store Keeper Required', '5 Year +', 'hr@medipakpharma.com', 'Computer', 'Lahore,Pkistan', 'Negotiable', '2016-05-27 00:00:00', '2016-06-11 00:00:00', 'jobspic/md.PNG', 'The candidate must have minimum 5 year plus experience in medical store and the age is 30+ qualification intermediate/graduate and other the candidate must have computer experience and operate this.They ensure proper scheduling, recordkeeping, and inventory control.  \r\nAbout company:  \r\nMedipak Limited, pioneer and trendsetter in infusion therapy life saving products, was established in 1982 under technical collaboration and know-how from M/s Fresenius AG, of Germany. It is the first integrated Infusion Solutions and Disposable Infusion Administration Sets manufacturing facility in the country. Over the years, through numerous expansions and foreign collaborations, Medipak has evolved into one of the top national pharmaceutical companies in Pakistan. We have collaborations with companies such as Fresenius AG ( Germany ), Baxter (USA), and Novartis (Switzerland) to name a few. We adhere to highest GMP standards at our manufacturing facility  and are ISO 9001 and ISO 14001 certified . Today, the company offers:\r\n', 1),
(16, 'wsphome', 'Hiring PHP Developer', '1 Year', 'nosharwan@rightjobs.pk', 'Ajax,JSON,Jquery, etc...', 'Lahore,Pakistan', '25K-40K', '2016-06-06 00:00:00', '2016-06-19 00:00:00', 'jobspic/Capture.PNG', 'A internationl company required a PHP developer at lahore office a candidate must have 1 year experience in development field and also must be proficient in javascript including AJAX,JSON,JQuery and MVC Sructures such as codeigniter or cake php.The candidate must have experience in wordpress,joomla,druple,OsCommerce,Zend framework,Wikis and  blogs.Its a software company that provide the online solution of software and other services like branded sms,social media markeeting ...etc.\r\nTiming:First Time(Day Shift)\r\nsalary negotiable on the expirience.The canidate have these skills then he apply for this job to click the apply button', 1),
(18, 'Government', 'Water and Power Development Authority WAPDA 04 July 2016 Jobs', 'NA', 'info@wapda.gov.pk', 'Well Menerd,Good Comunication Skills', 'Lahore,Pakistan', 'NA', '2016-07-04 00:00:00', '2016-07-18 00:00:00', 'jobspic/Jobs-in-Water-and-Power-Development-Authority-WAPDA-04-July-2016.jpg', 'WAPDA is inviting applications for the recruitment of suitable candidates to fill the below mentioned posts on one year contract basis\r\n(extendable) subject to satisfactory performance.\r\nOnly Local candidates can apply for the posts mentioned at Sr. No. 04 to 08 above.\r\nâ€¢ Candidates will enclose with application form attested copy of CN1C, domicile, qualification certificates / degrees and 02 x recent\r\npassport size photographs.\r\nâ€¢ The posts applied for may be written on top left side of the envelope,\r\nâ€¢ Candidates applying under employees children quota will enclose affidavit on non judicial paper that none of their brother / sister has been\r\nappointed against this quota in the past along with providing the documentary proof of employment of their father / mother in WAPDA.\r\nâ€¢ Only shortlisted candidates will be called for Test / Interview. No TA / DA will be admissible to candidates called for test / interview.\r\nâ€¢ WAPDA has right to reject any application and stop recruitment process at any stage without assigning any reason.\r\nâ€¢ Incomplete applications will not be entertained.\r\nâ€¢ Last date of submission of applications is\r\n18-07-2016.\r\nâ€¢ Eligible Candidates may send their applications on prescribed form to\r\nAddl: Director General (Establishment) HR&Admn WAPDA,\r\n301-WAPDA House.\r\nLahore. Application Forms can be downloaded from WAPDA Website\r\n(www.wapda.gov.pk)', 1),
(19, 'Information Technology', 'Multiple Jobs Opening in Saudi Arabia(IT)', 'NA', 'stshiring2016@outlook.com', 'Android,Web Developer,ISO', 'Saudi Arabia', 'Nill', '2016-07-09 00:00:00', '2016-08-01 00:00:00', 'jobspic/ddddd.PNG', 'STS is a startup IT Company located in Riyadh Saudi Arabia, we are focused to develop our in-house apps / solutions for the Saudi Arabian and Middle East market. STS is the part of a reputed group of companies in KSA.\r\nWe are looking for:\r\n-Senior android developer ( 4 to 6 year exp)\r\n-Junior android developer ( 2 to 3 year exp)\r\n-Senior IOS developer (4 to 6 year exp)\r\n-Junior IOS developer ( 2 to 3 year exp)\r\n-Full stack web developer ( 5 year exp)\r\n-Senior web developer (5 year exp)\r\nSTS is directly hiring capable resources from various countries and for that reason, selected candidates would not need to pay any services or Visa/ Ticket expenses. The company will bear all the expenses mentioned.\r\nJob Benefits:\r\nDirect hiring by company, all expenses of Visa/ Ticket will be paid by company.\r\nOne month paid annual vacation.\r\nFree return ticket to the homeland (once in year).\r\nOfficial working hourâ€™s compliance with Ministry of Labor.\r\nCompany accommodation (attractive location).\r\nAnnual bonuses on better performance.\r\nInterested candidates shall send their resumes to click apply button. ', 1),
(20, 'Information Technology', 'Required Software Engineer PHP(Fresh Graduate)', 'NA', 'job@novapextech.com', 'PHP,HTML, CSS 3, Bootstrap/Foundation', 'Lahore,Pakistan', 'Nill', '2016-07-06 00:00:00', '2016-07-26 00:00:00', 'jobspic/sdads.PNG', 'Novapex Software \r\nTechnologies(www.novapextech.com) is looking for a talented, self-motivated and solution provider PHP developer, who have excellent analytical and communication skills with a proven track record in PHP and Web 2.0 development. The candidate should have deep knowledge of PHP framework (Laravel/Phalcon); together with strong knowledge in front-end technologies HTML, CSS, JQuery, AJAX, Javascript libraries etc.\r\nNOTE: Fresh graduates with excellent skills in PHP and JQuery can also apply.\r\nQualifications:\r\nâ€¢ Excellent knowledge of PHP (Laravel/Phalcon).\r\nâ€¢ Excellent knowledge of HTML, CSS 3, Bootstrap/Foundation, Javascript/ Javascript Libraries, jQuery & jQuery plugins, AngluarJS, JSON\r\nâ€¢ Very good knowledge of Web Service standards (REST, WSDL etc),\r\nâ€¢ Very good understanding of OOP, IDE for PHP, Design patterns etc.\r\nâ€¢ Good knowledge of database design & concepts, MySQL and SQL\r\nâ€¢ Knowledge of any Wordpress will be plus point ( Wordpress Plugin Development, Wordpress Theme Development, Deep Understanding of CMS (Wordpress) Architecture )\r\nâ€¢ Good knowlege of Tools such as Adobe Photoshop, Adobe Dreamweaver \r\nNOTE: Salary is negotiable and will be based on your experience and skill set.\r\nPlease post your resumes to click apply button.', 1),
