(25, 'Asia', '2016-08-10 00:00:00', 'Lahore,Pakistan', 'newspic/Lahorehighcourt.jpg', 'Ishtiaq Ahmad Plea To Lahore High Court For Banning Indian Entertainment In Pakistan', 'Nowadays a topic which is under conversation is Kashmir Issue  which is now known by all over the world that how the peoples of Kashmir are facing the troubles given by Indian Army.they are killing people with different ways which a man could not even see.</br>\r\n\r\nWhy they are doing this cruelty with innocent people what they want anybody could say nothing this fight is from the independence when Pakistan came in map of world Then Gandhi and Quaid-e-Azam take decision that any little state have its own decision that in which country they wanted to include.</br>\r\n\r\nEvery state take decision by itself but when there was the matter  of Kashmir then India take decision by itself that they will include Kashmir with them but the people of Kashmir don,t want to include in India because Kashmir,s boundaries were combined with Pakistan not with India.but no one want to leave Kashmir but their were Muslims in number that this was the matter that Kashmir include in Pakistan but India never want till now.</br>\r\n\r\nThis war is continued and Kashmirs are fighting for their rights day by day peoples are killed by Indian Army with wild ways no one is there who could take action against them.United Nation is also silent about it.</br>\r\n\r\n\r\nSo there are many countries but no one can help our political leaders still silent about this matter why they can,t help those innocent.when United Nation have  responsibility to solve any problem then why these countries never mind this matter where many peoples killed every day which even much cruel.</br>\r\n\r\nOw Pakistan decide to ban those movies which are released in Pakistan because till now Pakistan was behaving normal but now it,s enough if they don,t have humanity then Pakistan will not also make sure their benefits which they can get from Pakistan