(26, 'Technology', '2016-08-11 00:00:00', 'Lahore,Pakistan', 'newspic/570f16b28fdad.jpg', 'Cybercrime Bill Which Is Passed On Sunday And What Are The Public Views.', 'Monday which was deadline for the approval so result announced for this approval which was that this bill has become a law of Pakistan.</br>\r\n \r\nSo this bill was  sent in national assembly when a bill was also sent for women rights this bill was passed but cyber crime bill was not passed because they want some amendments in this bill.so in last days it was again repeat in party for amendments then it was has deadline of Monday that it will be passed on Monday so it passed on Monday and finally become a law of land of Pakistan.</br>\r\n\r\nAccordingly this bill a person who is doing hacking of different accounts and different s posts on social media .frauds,hate speech and cyber terrorism will be punished according to this act.</br>\r\n\r\nA punishment for cyber terrorism is 14 years behind bar and child pornography will be sent behind bars for 7 years.there is fine of 5,000,000 for these punishments.the one more thing which is important and going faster on social media is posting of pictures without permission of any person will pay fine 1,000,000/- so some of them are more important because cyber crimes are growing fastly.</br>\r\n\r\n\r\nIt was also said that courts will assign these punishments to different security offices who will apply this as a rule and a person who is going against these rules will mostly punished according to constitution.</br>\r\n\r\nOne more thing which is highly growing on social media is hate content which now will be not allowed on internet because PTA have also authority according to this constitution that anybody could not upload hate content on social media.</br>\r\n\r\nReaction of people on this constitution was terrible about this bill different comments passed on social media that this is not good that this is only the cleverness of our politicians that people could say nothing about him on social media remain silent about all conditions of the country.</br>\r\n\r\nfacebook and twitter has got a number of hate comments on social media that we are against this bill this is rejected by all of us because it,s wrong that is only the why old nations that remain silent say nothing about the rulers.</br>\r\n\r\nAs protest many sounds on facebook and twitter that why this bill was passed by senate why they are not giving right to say something for our rights.we are making different speeches quotes for freedom to speak.we want this freedom.</br>\r\n\r\n\r\nSo decided by all peoples of Pakistan that this bill is not suitable for public we have also right of freedom to speak according to Pakistan constitution.so we are not going in favor of this bill we will not remain silent  Pakistani we have all rights so once again think about this constitution.</br>\r\n<h5>Team Views â€œWorld Solution Providerâ€.</h5></br>\r\n\r\nWe agree with this Cyber Crime bill except the one thing which is no any content on social media according to government because this is wrong people have full right to defend for giving their own suggestions so we are with our public which is right because this is one thing to motivate the people of Pakistan because our motive is to motivate Pakistan.', 1),
(27, 'Technology', '2016-08-12 00:00:00', 'Lahore,Pakistan', 'newspic/watsapp.jpg', 'What,s New About Whatsapp And Changings In Its Version To Prove It Best', 'There is vulgar in our societies that people ever try to read out the secret conversation of their friends and family members.which is immoral but people don,t care of this.</br>\r\n\r\nBut now their are different systems which are now activating to secure the chats and secret conversation.in 2016 there were different cases about privacies that different peoples accounts haked by hackers and there were cases to steal money by tracing password of any individual.</br>\r\n\r\nNow we are talking about the whats-app messages which privacies are going to be powerful wit making different strategies.</br>\r\n\r\nIn previous days there was a changing about end-to-end encryption it means there is no third person which could be applied and it can also show the  data which shared you on whatsapp.  This data mean all calls,messages and media could be seen by you and a person which you sharing this.\r\n\r\nIn this app we have no any sign out option so we have only the option to block any number.in this app we can just connect to our friends and family which have our number they knows about us but if any body have our number can contact to us any time till he have our contact.</br>\r\n\r\nIt was also in these changings that how we could fix the issue.</br>\r\n\r\nNow it was once again said that about a researcher that we can backtrack in our mobile phones</br>\r\nNow in this year it was also said about the whats-app that the privacy will be powerful like only sender and receiver and read out the messages except them no one will be able to read out the messages.</br>\r\n\r\n\r\nThis researcher also told that we can found these conversations by retraced that we have already deleted these chats.that loophole version is available in latest version.</br>\r\n\r\nIf we talk about the privacies then we can see that Brazil blocked w